scenes.description: A slideshow displaying numerous messages from fans supporting hololive English members for their 2nd concert, "Breaking Dimensions".
Title card showing the official hashtag and stating that the concert will begin soon.
An "Attention" slide providing guidelines for visitors, such as being aware of flashing lights and that cheering is allowed.
A series of slides showcasing various "Breaking Dimensions" concert merchandise, including clothing, penlights, and collectibles.
Continuation of the fan message slideshow.
